On a sensitive issue like this, it is only natural that our exchanges have sometimes been a little difficult.
I hope that they have been of some use. I certainly hope they have not done any damage.
As I approach the end of my term as a Commissioner â I underline âas a Commissionerâ â I have started going to the theatre again.
